Mega Launcher

Powers up aura and pulse moves.

Affected Moves

The following moves are affected by this ability.

Name Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
Aura Sphere 20 80 — The user lets loose a blast of aura power from deep within its body. This attack never misses.
Continuum Pulse 15 50 100 The user distorts spacetime. This move always goes first under Gravity.
Dark Pulse 15 80 100 The user releases a horrible aura full of dark thoughts. It may also make a target flinch.
Dragon Pulse 10 85 100 The target is attacked with a shock wave generated by the user's gaping mouth.
Eerie Energy 20 70 100 The user exudes sinister energy pulses. The move's power is doubled in Eerie Fog.
Heal Pulse 10 — — The user emits a healing pulse that restores the target's HP by up to half of its max HP.
Origin Pulse 10 110 85 Opposing Pokémon are hit with countless beams of light that glow a deep and brilliant blue.
Terrain Pulse 10 50 100 This move's type and power changes depending on the terrain when it's used.
Water Pulse 20 60 100 The user attacks the target with a pulsing blast of water. This may also confuse it.
